OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy with a chance of
OL,6,Foccasional showers, these mostly in
OL,7,Fthe north and over higher ground.
OL,8,FSunny intervals are likely too, these
OL,9,Fmost frequent later in the day.
OL,10,FRemaining rather breezy and feeling
OL,11,Fcooler than yesterday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny early evening showers
OL,14,Fsoon easing to leave a generally dry
OL,15,Fnight, although remaining rather
OL,16,Fcloudy. Winds easing and turning
OL,17,Frather cool for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
