OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSunday will be a fine day with
OL,6,Flight winds and a mix of fair weather
OL,7,Fcloud and sunny spells. Feeling warmer
OL,8,Ffor all.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,11,Fwith sunny spells on Monday. Becoming
OL,12,Fmore unsettled from Tuesday with rain
OL,13,For showers at times, turning windier,
OL,14,Fespecially by Wednesday. Remaining
OL,15,Frather warm throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
